dct_alternative_sm: Serenissimae Reipvblicae Genvensis dvcatvs et dominii nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Scala milliarium."
Index of place names on right.
Decorative cartouches, coat of arms, compass rose, rhumb lines, ship, sea monsters.
Dedication to Anonioto Sivori in cartouche on left.
Appears in Ortelius' Theatrum orbis terrarum, 1608, published by Vrients after Ortelius' death.
